ning: No Management: Team Lead This Company Describes Its Culture as: Detail-oriented -- quality and precision-focused Innovative -- innovative and risk-taking Aggressive -- competitive and growth-oriented Outcome-oriented -- results-focused with strong performance culture Stable -- traditional, stable, strong processes People-oriented -- supportive and fairness-focused Team-oriented -- cooperative and collaborative Schedule: Monday to Friday Company's website: https://syncfab.com/ Company's Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/syncfab Benefit Conditions: Waiting period may apply Work Remotely: Yes ", 
